			<sumFormula>-</sumFormula>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Sodium silicate, often called 'water glass', is the most important of the soluble silicates. It is ordinarily supplied as a colorless, viscous water solution. It can be used as a spin-on adhesive layer to bond glass to glass or silicon oxide covered silicon wafers. It is non-toxic but can pose harm to the skin and eyes. It can withstand temperatures of up to 1100 °C and increases the pH of the flotation cell. It is also known to have a powerful effect on deinking performance.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硅酸钠通常被称为 &quot;水玻璃&quot;，是最重要的可溶性硅酸盐。它通常以无色粘稠水溶液的形式供应。它可用作旋涂粘合剂层，将玻璃与玻璃或覆盖氧化硅的硅晶片粘合在一起。它无毒，但会对皮肤和眼睛造成伤害。它能承受高达 1100 °C 的温度，并能提高浮选池的 pH 值。众所周知，它对脱墨性能也有很大的影响。</common:generalComment>
